- Take the time to explore all the features and interactions within the Jukebox Demo.
- Consider the user experience and technical design aspects of the jukebox.

## 🏆 Bonus

If you have completed this activity, consider the following challenge to further your knowledge:

* Propose enhancements or new features for the jukebox use-case.
* Share your ideas with your peers or instructor.

## 📝 Notes

Engaging in the Jukebox Demo provides hands-on experience with a real-world application of edge computing and offers insights into innovative design and user experience.

